    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2015-11-03</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2016-01-04T19:46:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Reserve Transparency Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> This bill directs the Government Accountability Office to: (1) commence and complete an audit of the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System and of the Federal Reserve Banks within 12 months of enactment of this Act, and (2) report findings and conclusions to Congress within 90 days of completing the audit.</p> <p>The bill also repeals certain limitations upon such an audit.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
